 
<p>

In April, China froze the bank accounts of thousands of people because
the bank was in danger of bankruptcy.  Those people have effectively
lost their money, and may be broke, so they <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/jul/11/china-violent-clashes-at-protest-over-frozen-rural-bank-accounts">protested in the street</a>,
and <a href="/glossary.html#thug">thugs</a> came and beat them up.

 